name: Realme coolx Watch
content: Select from a combination of two designs and four colors to make your watch truly unique. With a one-button quick detach, it's easy to change the strap. Moreover, the watch weighs from 31g and is made from silicone, which is soft and skin-friendly, and doesn't stain easily.*

name: Noise Cool Smart watch
content:
ColorFit Pro 2 is the second generation of our most popular smartwatch, the ColorFit Pro. It
features a stylish design and a gorgeous 1.3" full touch colour display, as well as complete
health and activity tracking with 9 sports modes. Call, text & social media notifications, control
music playback and more features add further to the experience.
